#ifndef IEC_TYPES_H_FIRST

namespace IEC_STD {

// general types
typedef unsigned char ubyte;
typedef unsigned short uword;
typedef unsigned long udword;
typedef unsigned long long uldword;
typedef float real;
typedef double lreal;
typedef char string;

typedef char int8;
typedef short int16;
typedef long int32;

#if defined(__GNUC__)
typedef long long int64;
#elif defined(_MSC_VER)
typedef __int64 int64;
#else
#error "Unknown target!!!"
#endif

typedef IEC_STD::ubyte uint8;
typedef IEC_STD::uword uint16;
typedef IEC_STD::udword uint32;
typedef IEC_STD::uldword uint64;

typedef IEC_STD::int64 time;
typedef IEC_STD::int64 tod;
typedef IEC_STD::int64 time_of_day;
typedef IEC_STD::int64 dt;
typedef IEC_STD::int64 date_and_time;
typedef IEC_STD::int64 date;

#define IEC_BOOL bool
#define IEC_BYTE IEC_STD::ubyte
#define IEC_WORD IEC_STD::uword
#define IEC_DWORD IEC_STD::udword
#define IEC_LWORD IEC_STD::uldword
#define IEC_USINT IEC_STD::uint8
#define IEC_SINT IEC_STD::int8
#define IEC_UINT IEC_STD::uint16
#define IEC_INT IEC_STD::int16
#define IEC_UDINT IEC_STD::uint32
#define IEC_DINT IEC_STD::int32
#define IEC_ULINT IEC_STD::uint64
#define IEC_LINT IEC_STD::int64
#define IEC_REAL IEC_STD::real
#define IEC_LREAL IEC_STD::lreal
#define IEC_TIME IEC_STD::time

#if defined(__GNUC__)
#define __GNU_PACKED__ __attribute__((packed))
#elif defined(_MSC_VER)
#define __GNU_PACKED__
#else
#error "Unknown target!!!"
#endif

#if defined(_MSC_VER)
#pragma pack(push)
#pragma pack(1)
#endif

union qw_int32 {
struct __GNU_PACKED__ {
int32 mHi;
int32 mLo;
};
int64 mLint;
qw_int32( IEC_LINT& lintVal ) : mLint( lintVal ) {}
qw_int32( const IEC_LINT& lintVal ) : mLint( lintVal ) {}
};
union qw_uint32 {
struct __GNU_PACKED__ {
uint32 mHi;
uint32 mLo;
};
uint64 mULint;
qw_uint32( IEC_ULINT& uLintVal ) : mULint( uLintVal ) {}
qw_uint32( const IEC_ULINT& uLintVal ) : mULint( uLintVal ) {}
};

#if defined(_MSC_VER)
#pragma pack(pop)
#endif

union IEC_DWORD_REAL {
IEC_REAL mReal;
IEC_DWORD mDword;
IEC_DWORD_REAL( IEC_REAL rV ) : mReal( rV ) {}
IEC_DWORD_REAL( IEC_DWORD rV ) : mDword( rV ) {}
};

union IEC_LWORD_LREAL {
IEC_LREAL mLReal;
IEC_LWORD mLword;
IEC_LWORD_LREAL( IEC_LREAL& rV ) : mLReal( rV ) {}
IEC_LWORD_LREAL( IEC_LWORD& rV ) : mLword( rV ) {}
IEC_LWORD_LREAL( const IEC_LREAL& rV ) : mLReal( rV ) {}
IEC_LWORD_LREAL( const IEC_LWORD& rV ) : mLword( rV ) {}
};
